                        <div class="collapse" id="why-should-i-use-you">
                            <p>Unlike other insurers, we're less focused on profit, and more focused on giving customers value.  Our mission is to make insurance better and cheaper for honest people,  and that's why we've developed clever anti-fraud tech that makes your life easier. Plus we're the only insurer that gives you <a href="#social-insurance-and-reward-pot" class="scroll-to" data-scroll-to-anchor="#social-insurance-and-reward-pot" data-scroll-to-focus="#social-insurance-and-reward-pot">money back</a>.</p>
