                        <div class="collapse" id="what-am-i-covered-for">
                            <p>We believe that trust starts by us being clear with you about what is covered and what is not covered. If you have a valid claim we’ll have your back and we won't hide behind the small print unlike some insurance providers do.</p>
                            <p>We have one policy that covers you for:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Loss &amp; Theft</li>
                                <li>Accidental Damage</li>
                                <li>Out of warranty breakdown</li>
                                <li>Travel globally travel for up to 90 days</li>
                                <li>Accessories up to &pound;100 with a loss of theft claim</li>
                                <li>Unauthorised network charges up to &pound;1000 related to approved loss or theft claim, as long as your network was notified within 24hrs of the loss or theft</li>
