                            <ul>
                                <li><mark>Proof of purchase if you have not validated your phone with our app</mark></li>
                                <li><mark>Usage report from your network</mark></li>
                                <li><mark>Police report if stolen</mark></li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <h3>
